# 🐾 Digital Pet Simulator

This is a fun and interactive **object-oriented Python program** that simulates caring for a virtual pet. Your digital pet has hunger, energy, and happiness levels — and it can even learn tricks! You can feed it, play with it, let it sleep, and monitor its status.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🍽️ Feed the pet to reduce hunger
- 💤 Let it sleep to restore energy
- 🎲 Play to increase happiness (while using energy & increasing hunger)
- 🧠 Train it to learn cool tricks
- 📊 Check its current status
- 📚 View all learned tricks

---

## 🧠 OOP Concepts Demonstrated

This project is a great demonstration of core **object-oriented programming (OOP)** concepts:

- ✅ **Class & Object creation**
- ✅ **Encapsulation** using methods
- ✅ **Attribute state tracking** (e.g. hunger, energy, happiness)
- ✅ **Method interaction** to modify internal state

---

